  "3077570": {
    "name": "萌萌夹击",
    "steam_appid": 3077570,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077570/extras/82efea1f6e51d4a1cea71c64bf142c91.avif?t=1769562204\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077570/extras_big/82efea1f6e51d4a1cea71c64bf142c91.avif?t=1769562204 width=800 height=141 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>▼由美腿演奏的，新感觉动作游戏！▼</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以简单的操作驾驭美丽的双腿，将从画面深处袭来的魂等敌人逐一击破！跟着动感的节拍，把魂夹住，净化魂…《萌萌夹击》就是这样一款通过崭新的题材打造的，爽快感满满的节奏游戏！！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>▼个性炸裂！三位“美腿战士”正等待着你！▼</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这混沌的世界中，存在着拥有独一无二净化之力的“美腿战士”们。敬请期待她们可爱又强大的活跃表现！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077570/extras/0e999f705b62f427bd34007e7845c49d.webp?t=1769562204\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077570/extras/0e999f705b62f427bd34007e7845c49d.poster.avif?t=1769562204\" class=\"bb_img\" width=250 height=250 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💎 <strong>黛雅（自信爆棚、气场全开、光彩夺目、少女永驻）</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“魅惑、征服、支配——完美自我包装的究极美腿”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“宝石少女”黛雅，闪耀着自信与品味！对她而言，“可爱”即是正义，是究极的自我展现。她以完美打磨的“大腿”为武器，为将世界染上只属于她的“可爱”色彩，今天也依旧战斗、依旧魅惑！目标是成为NO.1品牌的总裁，这份野心无人能挡！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077570/extras/dcbeb8682f0276d9e0c882ebcbc201dd.webp?t=1769562204\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077570/extras/dcbeb8682f0276d9e0c882ebcbc201dd.poster.avif?t=1769562204\" class=\"bb_img\" width=250 height=250 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💜 <strong>清香（羞涩可爱、小鹿乱撞、紧锁之心、博爱修女）</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“渴望被拯救，亦渴望拯救他人——内在翻涌的爱之囚笼大腿”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在作为圣女的职责与“渴望被他人需要”的真切心愿之间摇摆不定的内向修女“清香”。在那端庄的修女服之下所隐藏的“大腿”，是治愈世界的慈爱之力，也是时而将自身囚禁的激情化成的“爱之囚笼”。她想用这双腿抓住的，究竟是世界的和平，还是属于自己的微小幸福——。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077570/extras/fb759e0d7d8e464b80f8b40c4aef6a77.webp?t=1769562204\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077570/extras/fb759e0d7d8e464b80f8b40c4aef6a77.poster.avif?t=1769562204\" class=\"bb_img\" width=250 height=250 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌞 <strong>光（古灵精怪、闪耀新星、笑容开朗、乐天派旅人）</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“破坏也毫无罪恶感——天真烂漫的粉碎一切大腿”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >心中只怀着“想让大家露出笑容！”这一纯粹的愿望，今天也依旧环游世界的天真烂漫的旅人光！为了寻找失踪的姐姐，无论任何困难都用引以为傲的“强化大腿”豪迈地粉碎！如太阳般开朗的她的破坏力，当然也完全没有任何恶意与罪恶感！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077570/extras/b976087e28824dfbe396562bf0f59d38.avif?t=1769562204\" width=1138 height=200 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>▼人人都能上手！核心玩法完全解说！▼</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >基本操作只有「夹住」和「踢」两个动作！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >伴随节奏从画面深处飞来的，是三种各具特色的目标。用正确的动作精准应对吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此外，本作还搭载了可以享受<strong>美腿战士故事的剧情模式</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >推进剧情即可解锁新曲目，在演奏游戏中挑战还能提升与角色的亲密度。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的玩法将加深彼此的关系，并对故事的发展产生影响。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一边享受「大腿 × 音乐节奏游戏」，一边与心仪的角色一起拯救世界吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077570/extras/a85c828aa0fc3292b78e237b9cdee8cd.poster.avif?t=1769562204\" width=874 height=492 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077570/extras/a85c828aa0fc3292b78e237b9cdee8cd.webm?t=1769562204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077570/extras/a85c828aa0fc3292b78e237b9cdee8cd.mp4?t=1769562204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>👻飞来的《魂》</strong>，请看准时机用大腿温柔地夹住并净化！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077570/extras/86e6003d718f08955c0ac040ec0c7afb.poster.avif?t=1769562204\" width=874 height=492 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077570/extras/86e6003d718f08955c0ac040ec0c7afb.webm?t=1769562204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077570/extras/86e6003d718f08955c0ac040ec0c7afb.mp4?t=1769562204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">🦠但是，偶尔<strong>混进来的《病毒》</strong>，就用大腿飞踢来击退！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077570/extras/b6f7a436c0df5679dade7cdea3081067.poster.avif?t=1769562204\" width=874 height=492 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077570/extras/b6f7a436c0df5679dade7cdea3081067.webm?t=1769562204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077570/extras/b6f7a436c0df5679dade7cdea3081067.mp4?t=1769562204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">🐈哎呀，对<strong>可爱的《猫咪》</strong>…可不能攻击它哦！<br>请悄悄地把膝盖借给它，让它心满意足地慢慢休息吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“夹击净化+飞踢击破+偶尔疼爱猫咪（？）”——就是这么简单粗暴又内涵丰富的玩法…！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077570/extras/9340e51a2c4839a14eee74cee1880c33.avif?t=1769562204\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077570/extras_big/9340e51a2c4839a14eee74cee1880c33.avif?t=1769562204 width=800 height=141 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>▼来自制作人的全部爱与「大腿」▼</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SKOOTA GAMES 开发团队，正面迎接了人类共同的癖好（如今已是文化）。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大腿——那是温柔与力量的象征。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >倾尽所有的大腿，只献给你——。</p>",
